snippet: Mr. Holmes led NASA’s manned spaceflight program during a period that included John Glenn’s orbit of Earth and helped set the stage for the first moon landing.
abstract: D Brainerd Holmes, who led NASA’s manned spaceflight program during period that included John Glenn’s historic orbit of Earth and helped set stage for first moon landing, dies at age 91.
lead_paragraph: Mr. Holmes led NASA’s manned spaceflight program during a period that included John Glenn’s orbit of Earth and helped set the stage for the first moon landing.

headline.seo: D. Brainerd Holmes, Top NASA Official, Dies at 91
headline.main: D. Brainerd Holmes, a Leader in Space Race, Dies at 91
headline.print_headline: D. Brainerd Holmes, 91, a Leader in Space Race, Dies
